<author>hạny rwmạny, hạny rwmạny</author>
<title>kdẖbwạ mn qạlwạ ạ̹ny wḥyd</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 kdẖbwạ .. mn qạlwạ ạ̹ny wḥyd .. fy ạlạ̉rḍ dwn snyd
 mn hzạ̉wạ mn ạ̹ymạny .. brby ạlmjyd
 kdẖbwạ .. mn zyfwạ ạlklmạt .. wạstslmwạ lldẖạt
 wạ̉sẖạʿwạ ạ̉n ạllh .. bʿyduⁿ bʿyduⁿ kmạ ạlsmạwạt .. kdẖbwạ
 (fạllh yrʿạny kmạ .. yrʿy̱ ạlạ̉b ạlạ̉ṭfạl
 wạllh yḥmyny ạ̹dẖạ .. sạʾt by ạlạ̉ḥwạl)2
 (wạ̹lhy fy qrby .. ysẖbʿny bạlḥb)2
 wynyr ly drby .. wyḥqq ạlạ̉mạl</lyrics>
</song>